==Description==
The '''Red Shard''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The Red Shard can be used with [[Quest Points]] {{Questpoints}} to obtain items from [[Shard Trader|Shard Traders]].

==Mine Layout==
The Red Shard appears in the Underground as a 3x3 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:RedShardMine.png|100px]]

==Trades==
Red Shards can be used to purchase the following items:
